{
 "name": "RPlog_Outpost_Ambush",
 "title": "Outpost Ambush",
 "summary": "On a quiet patrol, the Imperial TIE pilots Fortune and Jonas are ambushed by a New Republic Ghost Squadron flight escorting a B-wing on a mission to destroy an Imperial sensor drone. Jonas, grinning, locks into a grueling dogfight with a familiar foe, the Zabrak flying Ghost 8, the two evenly matched pilots trading fire, rolls, and missiles across the void. While the duel rages, the Republic's strategy succeeds: the B-wing Dagger 3 slips through to pound the sensor drone until it erupts in flame and breaks apart. With the mission accomplished and the rebel flight ordered to withdraw, a frustrated Jonas gives chase too hastily, failing to notice the danger as the engagement winds down.",
